第1讲：拼音

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/appEOYSm4kc8307/a_5c0778687b133_cJ3Oh6KC

<section style="white-space: normal;"><section style="border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="border-style: solid; -webkit-border-image: url(&#39;http://mpt.135editor.com/mmbiz_png/z9433rAGTDecZ8215cOibjjBHbLrMARg1JDibVvialwoDQiczIV6gpibDib7aXcnfwYb9B6Qa4ycNCsZVibk5s59VNAtA/0?wx_fmt=png&#39;) 15 fill; border-width: 15px; padding: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">有位青年农民进城办事，需要住旅馆。他问路人：“同志，雷馆有没有？”路人一听，立即射出警惕的目光，厉声问道：“雷管是国家禁止私人买卖的爆炸品，你要它干什么？”并且拿出手机准备报警。经过再三解释，<strong>方知是青年农民发音不准，将“旅馆”说成“雷管”。</strong></span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;"><strong><br/></strong></span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">像这样因为发音不清造成不好的后果在生活中经常发生。<strong>因为发音不准，吐字不清，不仅会造成他人对自己的误解，而且会使得自己的自卑心无限放大。</strong></span></p></section></section></section><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appEOYSm4kc8307/image/ueditor/12499900_1543993058.com/timg"/></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">而从医学方面来看，发音不清竟然能引起“疾病”！</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">究竟不科学的发声方式会导致什么样的后果呢？</span><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><br/></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">据报道，有一名家长因为自己的孩子一直发音不清楚，而且声音嘶哑于是带孩子去医院查看。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">本身并没有引起重视的发音不清，却被医生诊断为“声带小结”，<span style="text-indent: 28px;">多因长期发声不当造成的后果。</span></span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px; text-indent: 28px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="text-indent: 28px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">这名家长十分懊悔，孩子发音不好，音调不准确从未当回事，还以为是成长时期必经的一个阶段，<strong>没想到这竟然会造成“疾病”！</strong></span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center;"><span style="text-indent: 28px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appEOYSm4kc8307/image/ueditor/27929100_1543993058.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="u=2100973106,3419576519&amp;fm=27&amp;gp=0.jpg"/></span></p><section style="border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static;"><section style="width: 2.5em; margin-left: auto;"><section style="width: 2.5em; border-top: 1px solid rgb(158, 158, 158); box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="height: 1.4em; border-left: 1px solid rgb(158, 158, 158); margin-top: -0.5em; margin-left: 2em; box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section><section style="padding-right: 1em; padding-left: 1em; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="padding: 10px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(160, 160, 160); line-height: 1.8; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">前段时间出过这样一条新闻，<span style="text-align: justify;">一名17岁的女孩去西班牙旅行。他们准备尝试一下惊险刺激的蹦极项目，女孩已经在自己的身上绑上了绳子。这时，她的西班牙教练用英语告诉她：“别跳！”（No jump）。由于这位西班牙教练的<strong>发音实在是太差</strong>了，女孩听成了：“现在就跳。”（Now jump）最终，导致其意外死亡。</span></span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><br/></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: justify;">不管英语还是中文，只要发音不准，在紧要关头也是非常致命。</span></strong></span></p></section></section><section style="height: 1.4em; border-left: 1px solid rgb(158, 158, 158); margin-bottom: -0.5em; margin-left: 0.5em; box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="width: 2.5em; border-top: 1px solid rgb(158, 158, 158); box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><br/></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; text-indent: 28px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">试想一下：<br/></span></p></section><section style="border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;"><section style="border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><br/></p><section style="display: inline-block; width: 665.139px; vertical-align: top;"><section style="position: static;"><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 280.375px;"><section style="position: static;"><section style="margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; position: static;"><section style="border-top: 1px dotted rgb(223, 223, 223); box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section></section><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 104.344px;"><section style="position: static;"><section style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 0.8; position: static;"><section style="width: 0px; display: inline-block; border-top: 0.8em solid rgb(187, 227, 197); box-sizing: border-box; border-left: 0.7em solid transparent !important; border-right: 0.7em solid transparent !important;"></section></section></section></section><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; width: 280.375px;"><section style="position: static;"><section style="margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; position: static;"><section style="border-top: 1px dotted rgb(223, 223, 223); box-sizing: border-box;"></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static;"><section style="text-align: justify; letter-spacing: 0px; line-height: 2; padding-right: 10px; padding-left: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin: 0.63em 15px 1.8em; color: rgb(25, 25, 25); font-size: 14px; border: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;"><span style="border: 0px;">当你来到一个完全陌生的</span>城市，遇到了陌生的人，因为自己的普通话不标准，使得别人根本听不懂自己到底在讲什么，你可能会产生误会甚至遇到危险；</span></p><p style="margin: 0.63em 15px 1.8em; color: rgb(25, 25, 25); font-size: 14px; border: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="border: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">当你在面试的时候因为自己的发音奇怪，再好的能力面试官都不会让你通过，团队中沟通顺畅很重要；</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; color: rgb(160, 160, 160); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">领导汇报你的发音里带着口音，第一显得土，第二营销报告效果，你会失去第二次发言的机会；</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; color: rgb(160, 160, 160); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">很多人学英语很困难无法坚持，但是研究发现，能够正确的发音，讲一口纯正普通话，对于英语口语有着非常大帮助；</span></span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><br/></span></span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><span style="font-size: 15px;">小孩子从小讲一口普通话非常关键，气质、学习、交朋友……有着极大的帮助！</span></span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; color: rgb(160, 160, 160); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><br/></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; color: rgb(160, 160, 160); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">跟着小白学发音，讲一口不费力、且标准的普通话！</span></p></section></section></section></section><section style="border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box;"><section><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; display: inline-block; width: 300px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><img title="佛教 浮云花纹 分割线" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appEOYSm4kc8307/image/ueditor/38816400_1543993058.com/mmbiz_png/un1liav7ojicjviaymlirhxoaugccq50zqc4bjxcqlqlohcichfhpiaymt5wob5iauagibsckwncdq50fmgln4vmvl3g/0" style="width: 300px; display: inline;"/></p></section><section><p style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; border-color: rgb(216, 40, 33); line-height: normal;"><br/></p></section></section><p style="margin: 0.63em 15px 1.8em; border: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(25, 25, 25); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appEOYSm4kc8307/image/ueditor/62148000_1543993058.jpg" alt="48.jpg"/></span></p><p style="margin: 0.63em 15px 1.8em; border: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(25, 25, 25); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">语言学家张志公先生说：“口头语言能力高，不是指‘口若悬河’地说个不停，也不是指辞藻美丽，才华出众，更不是孔夫子说的‘巧言令色’，而是指能用基本准确的标准话，即普通话，有力而得体地达到说话目的。”</span></p><p style="margin: 0.63em 15px 1.8em; border: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(25, 25, 25); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">很多人都会羡慕播音员、主持人拥有如此出众的普通话技巧，会羡慕他们是怎么说出一口让人听起来如此舒服的话。</span></p><section style="border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><br/></p><section style="display: inline-block;"><img title="金属质感分割线" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appEOYSm4kc8307/image/ueditor/76588900_1543993058.com/mmbiz/czv2hrpuapjeiibb1uyw1vmpzscnxrekzvxeh23qb9kgpqfq3uoyby3m93pcfounrvjkyvrtfvxmworbbuwaz4a/0" style="display: inline;"/></section><p><br/></p></section><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">声音悦耳、吐字清晰是正确言说的基础。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">据资料统计，人每天用于说话的时间平均是一小时，这样人一生中用于说话的时间累计可达两年半左右，甚至更长。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><br/></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">我们知道，说话是人的本能之一，更是一种极为重要的人类活动。我们只有反复练习和实践，坚决矫正我们以往发音和吐字等方面的不良习惯，<span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><strong>“如何吐字清晰”“如何说话让人听得舒服”这些问题就一定能够迎刃而解的。</strong></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0.63em 15px 1.8em; border: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(25, 25, 25); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0.63em 15px 1.8em; border: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(25, 25, 25); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appEOYSm4kc8307/image/ueditor/91319000_1543993058.jpeg" alt="146347510910575980.JPEG"/></span></p><p style="margin: 0.63em 15px 1.8em; border: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(25, 25, 25); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="border: 0px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">你是否还在为说不好普通话而自卑？</span></p><p style="margin: 0.63em 15px 1.8em; border: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(25, 25, 25); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="border: 0px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">是否还在羡慕播音员字正腔圆的普通话？</span></p><p style="margin: 0.63em 15px 1.8em; border: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(25, 25, 25); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">是否想做到说话让人听得舒服？</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; border: 0px none; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><br/></p><section style="display: inline-block;"><img title="形状分割线" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appEOYSm4kc8307/image/ueditor/3839000_1543993059.com/mmbiz_png/czv2hrpuapgyrpmmvayp0giuibunfykj4gzk2jrv8zntwldvict0ice1lq5krjv46yiannwzbxcibvwiauzmnhbk0ebg/0" style="display: inline;"/></section><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p style="margin: 0.63em 15px 1.8em; border: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(25, 25, 25); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">400万字专业女主播——小白</span></p><p style="margin: 0.63em 15px 1.8em; border: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(25, 25, 25); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">她将用最高效的方式，</span></p><p style="margin: 0.63em 15px 1.8em; border: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(25, 25, 25); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">带大家从<strong>声母、韵母、辨音练习开始学起</strong>，</span></p><p style="margin: 0.63em 15px 1.8em; border: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(25, 25, 25); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">为大家开辟一条<span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong>高性价比的普通话提升、</strong></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0.63em 15px 1.8em; border: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(25, 25, 25); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;"><strong>说话能够让人听得舒服、</strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0.63em 15px 1.8em; border: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(25, 25, 25); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;"><strong>主持人语言艺术提高之路。</strong></span></p><section><section style="border: 0px none; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="padding: 10px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; border: 0px none; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><br/></p><section style="width: 1em; height: 1em; display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; border-radius: 100%; margin-top: 0.7em; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(252, 146, 43); box-sizing: border-box;"></section><section style="display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; padding-right: 5px; padding-left: 5px; margin-right: 5px; margin-left: 5px; border-radius: 0.5em; font-size: 1.2em; font-family: inherit; text-decoration: inherit; color: inherit; height: 2em; line-height: 2em; border-color: rgb(252, 43, 64); max-width: 80%; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="color: inherit;"><span style="color: rgb