0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(25, 25, 25); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="border: 0px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">普通话发音精准，<strong>为自身形象加分</strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0.63em 15px 1.8em; border: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(25, 25, 25); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="border: 0px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">全面系统地指导，<strong>有助你迅速提高</strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0.63em 15px 1.8em; border: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(25, 25, 25); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="border: 0px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">流利说出普通话，<strong>发音不再是难题</strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0.63em 15px 1.8em; border: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(25, 25, 25); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="border: 0px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">提升声音的颜值，<strong>成为全场的焦点</strong></span></p></section></section><p><br/></p></section></section><p><br/></p>

第11讲：如何写好主持词

