etter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">2、&nbsp;&nbsp;韵母辨音</span></p><p><br/></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;"><strong>第二课&nbsp;</strong><strong>基础只是部分-</strong><strong>声调以及发声技巧</strong></span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">（四）&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;声调</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">（五）&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;音变</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">1、&nbsp;&nbsp;变调</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">2、&nbsp;&nbsp;轻声</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">3、&nbsp;&nbsp;儿化</span></p><p><br/></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">（六）&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;发声技巧</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">1、&nbsp;&nbsp;气息训练</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">2、&nbsp;&nbsp;共鸣训练</span></p><p style="margin-r