amily: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">1、&nbsp;&nbsp;重音</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">2、&nbsp;&nbsp;停顿</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">3、&nbsp;&nbsp;语调升降</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">4、&nbsp;&nbsp;语速</span></p><p><br/></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;"><strong>第四课&nbsp;</strong><strong>如何当好一名主持人</strong></span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">四、主持人的语言规范</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">（一）语言使用的常见错误</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">1、用词不当</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">2、方言味太重</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">3、语音错误</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">（二）主持人语言的基本要求</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">1、语音标准</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">2、用语准确</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">3、出色口语表达</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">（三）主持的语言艺术</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">1、语言通顺流畅</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">2、学会让日常语言艺术化</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">3、幽默</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">4、巧用比喻、夸张</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">5、&nbsp;&nbsp;提高语言修养</span></p><p><br/></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">五、主持人的基本仪态、礼仪</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">（一）基本仪态</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">1、表情</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">2、姿态</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">3、手势</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">4、主持的三要和三忌</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">（二）基本礼仪</span></p><p><br/></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">六、主持人的心理素质</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">1、自信很重要</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">2、学会自我感情控制</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">3、训练强大心理素质</span></p><p><br/></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">七、怎么写好主持词</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">1、最好一开场就吸引住观众</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">2、中间部分</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">3、拒绝虎头蛇尾</span></p><p><br/></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;"><strong>第五课&nbsp;</strong><strong>技能训练</strong></span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">技能训练部分</span></p><ul class=" list-paddingleft-2" style="width: 572.76px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><li><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">观察能力训练</span></p></li></ul><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">1、&nbsp;&nbsp;动物的观察</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">2、&nbsp;&nbsp;物品的观察</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">3、&nbsp;&nbsp;人物的观察</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">4、&nbsp;&nbsp;观察能力提高练习</span></p><ul class=" list-paddingleft-2" style="width: 572.76px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><li><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">模仿能力训练</span></p></li></ul><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">1、&nbsp;&nbsp;模仿动物</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">2、&nbsp;&nbsp;模仿人物</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">3、&nbsp;&nbsp;情景模仿</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">4、&nbsp;&nbsp;模仿能力练习</span></p><ul class=" list-paddingleft-2" style="width: 572.76px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><li><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">语言表达能力训练</span></p></li></ul><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">1、&nbsp;&nbsp;复述故事</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">2、&nbsp;&nbsp;看图说话</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">3、&nbsp;&nbsp;描述人物、动物和物品</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">4、&nbsp;&nbsp;完整地叙述一件身边的事</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">5、&nbsp;&nbsp;叙述大家一起游戏的过程</span></p><ul class=" list-paddingleft-2" style="width: 572.76px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><li><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">想象能力训练</span></p></li></ul><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">1、&nbsp;&nbsp;猜谜语</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">2、&nbsp;&nbsp;头脑风暴</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">3、&nbsp;&nbsp;续编故事</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">4、&nbsp;&nbsp;故事新编</span></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">5、&nbsp;&nbsp;联想编故事</span></p><ul class=" list-paddingleft-2" style="width: 572.76px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px;"><li><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: left;"><span st