 15px;">因为有着方言音而自卑，想要<strong>系统学习普通话</strong>的人；</span></p><p style="margin: 0.63em 15px 1.8em; border: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(25, 25, 25); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="border: 0px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">经常<strong>使用普通话</strong>的人（如讲师、培训师、想要晋升的主持人和主播等）；</span></p><p style="margin: 0.63em 15px 1.8em; border: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(25, 25, 25); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="border: 0px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">想要提升口才，增强声音表现力，<strong>为人生和职场加分</strong>的人。</span></p><p style="margin: 10px 5px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.5em;"><br/></p><p style="margin-right: 15px; margin-left: 15px; border: 0px none; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><br/></p><section style="display: inline-block; border-radius: 8px; background-color: rgb(240, 133, 144); padding: 5px; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="padding-top: 3px; padding-bottom: 3px; padding-left: 30px; color: rgb(254, 254, 254); border-radius: 8px; background-image: url(&#39;http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appEOYSm4kc8307/image/ueditor/10662900_1543993058.com/mmbiz_png/un1liav7ojichv6keghmuia8df4xqficzeppahyboejufxv1z88jl3nkrnayzby57linoibeae6wn4j6oujql3m7kg/0?wx_fmt=png&#39;); background-size: 30px; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-position: left center; box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="padding-left: 10px; letter-spacing: 1px; box-sizing: border-box;"><p class="135brush"><span style="font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;"><strong>你将收获什么</strong></span></p></section></section></section><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p style="margin: 0.63em 15px 1.8em; border: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(25, 25, 25); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="border: 0px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">普通话发音精准，<strong>为自身形象加分</strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0.63em 15px 1.8em; border: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(25, 25, 25); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="border: 0px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">全面系统地指导，<strong>有助你迅速提高</strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0.63em 15px 1.8em; border: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(25, 25, 25); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="border: 0px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">流利说出普通话，<strong>发音不再是难题</strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0.63em 15px 1.8em; border: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(25, 25, 25); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 1.5px;"><span style="border: 0px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 15px;">提升声音的颜值，<strong>成为全场的焦点</strong></span></p></section></section><p><br/></p></section></section><p><br/></p>

